export class LoaderComponent implements OnInit {
  ngOnInit() {
        setInterval(() => {
        }, 100)
  }

  @select((state) => {return state.loader.counter}) loaderCounter$: Observable<number>;
}
```

It seams if the observable change origin is out of angular application, angular is not considering its change.

Problem originally reported on angular-redux https://github.com/angular-redux/platform/issues/112

